ent star formation rate differs from the\nlocal mass cooling rate is consistent with recent simulations of episodic AGN\nfeedback and star formation in a cluster atmosphere.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 25 Dec 2016 21:41:49 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 28 Dec 2016 23:52:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-02-08"}
